Job Description
We are seeking to recruit on behalf of their client a Corporate HSE Manager who will be based in Abu Dhabi, UAE, and will be representing the client’s group of companies and visiting various locations worldwide:-
THIS ROLE IS RESPONSIBLE FOR MANAGING AND CO-ORDINATING ACTIVITIES RELATING TO THE ONGOING DEVELOPMENT, IMPLEMENTATION, AND COMPLIANCE MONITORING OF APPROVED GROUP HEALTH, SAFETY, AND ENVIRONMENT (HSE), SECURITY, FIRE PREVENTION AND HSE TRAINING PROGRAMS FOR ALL CLIENT GROUP PROJECTS AND FACILITIES, WITH A STRONG EMPHASIS ON CHAMPIONING HSE AWARENESS THROUGHOUT THE ORGANISATION AND ENSURING COMPLIANCE WITH OHSAS 18001 AND ISO 14001.THERE WILL BE EMPHASIS ON REFINING AND REINFORCING THE HSE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM AND HSE PROGRAMS AND CHAMPIONING GREATER HSE AWARENESS THROUGHOUT THE ORGANISATION. THE TRAINING, DEVELOPMENT AND MOTIVATION OF COMPETENT HSE STAFF ARE ALSO A MAJOR RESPONSIBILITY.
IF YOU WISH TO BE CONSIDERED FOR THIS POSITION, PLEASE SEND A DETAILED UPDATED CV/RESUME IN MICROSOFT WORD FORMAT
